<div class="panel-body articles">

<h1 class="article_heading">
Now Introducing Guess the Word</h1>
    <h2 class="news_date">Posted on: <span>Tuesday, March 15th, 2022</span></h2>
<div class="tagline">
</div>

<div class="article_content">

<!--div class="news_featured_image"> 								<img src="images/cubeswapbanner.png" /></div-->

<p><h3 style="text-align: left;" align="center"><span lang="EN">Guess the daily 5-letter word in this stunnning new puzzle game in 6 tries!</span></h3>
<h2 align="center"></h2>
<strong><span lang="EN">WEST LONG BRANCH, New Jersey — March 15, 2022 — </span></strong><span lang="EN">Leading game publisher Mad Lemons today announced the release of their newest hit game, <strong>Guess the Word</strong>. In this game, you need to guess the Word of the Day in 24 hours! Each word is 5 letters and you only have 6 guesses. Can you reach the highest score?</span>
<br>&nbsp;<br>
<p>- GUESS a new word everyday!</p>

<p>- COMPARE your scores to your friend. Who will Guess the Word first?</p>

<p>- TRACK your statistics and get a high streak!</p>

	<p>- NEW WORDS added weekly to the seletion, so every day will have a different word and challenge! The game is always getting better.</p>

<p>- CHALLENGE YOURSELF in Hard Mode, where you must use all hints in your next guesses!</p>

<p>- PLAY in DARK or LIGHT mode, at day or night!</p>

<p>How to Play:</p>
<p>In this game, you need to guess the word of the day. The word is unversal for all players and resets daily. As you guess words, you will get hints. But be careful! You only have 6 guesses!</p>
<p>- GREEN means that the letter is in the word and in the correct spot.</p>
<p>- YELLOW means that the letter is in the word, but in the incorrect spot.</p>
<p>- GRAY means that the letter is not in the word.</p>

<p>Can you get the highest streak?</p>
	<br>&nbsp;<br>
<br>&nbsp;<br>
<strong>About Mad Lemons</strong>
<p>Since 2015, Mad Lemons has published over 16 games, such as <i>Ball Maze Rolling Challenge</i>, <i>Ball Bounce Challenge</i>, <i>Bouncy</i>, <i>Casino Fever</i>, <i>Jumping Mania</i>, and most recently <i>Dragon Challenge</p>. For more information, please visit our website!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</div>
</div>
